  <num>4-754.55</num>
  <heading>Retaliation prohibited.</heading>
  <text>No person shall retaliate against a person who brings a complaint or provides information to the Shelter Monitoring Unit ("Unit") relevant to the performance of its duties. The Unit shall report any violation of this section to the Interagency Council and the Office of the Inspector General.</text>
